; FontAwesome Pro lives ONLY here — the app itself has no @fortawesome dependency.
; Installing this dev tool pulls the Pro icon packages from the private registry,
; so it needs a FontAwesome Pro token in FONTAWESOME_NPM_AUTH_TOKEN (the same one
; the repo root used to require). Load it from the repo's gitignored .env first:
;   set -a; . ../../.env; set +a; npm install
@fortawesome:registry=https://npm.fontawesome.com/
//npm.fontawesome.com/:_authToken=${FONTAWESOME_NPM_AUTH_TOKEN}
